#. [message]: id=Kromire
#: Kromire/scenarios/1Therian_Village.cfg:213
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hurry slave, we need to slay their leader without alerting their guard. If "
"we can take the keep, we can turn the peasants to our side. Do not alert "
"them prematurely. If you must fight, kill them before they can so much as "
"squeak."
msgstr ""
"En avant, serviteur ! Nous devons abattre leur chef sans alerter la garde. "
"Lorsque nous tiendrons le donjon, nous pourrons retourner les paysans de "
"notre côté. Ne déclenche pas l'alarme top tôt et si tu dois en combattre, "
"tue-les avant qu'ils n'émettent un seul murmure."

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Kromire/scenarios/1Therian_Village.cfg:226
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You! Foul creature, what are you doing here? Do you not know that the "
"celestials are coming? They will hew all your kind to the ground!"
msgstr ""
"Vous êtes fous de trainer par ici ! Vous ne savez pas que les Célestains "
"arrivent ? Ils vont vous réduire en poussière tout autant que vous êtes."

#. [message]: id=Kromire
#: Kromire/scenarios/1Therian_Village.cfg:230
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Oh, no worries... friend. We intend to be prepared for them, and your "
"village is a part of the preparation. You should feel duly honored."
msgstr ""
"Oh, ne crains rien, l'ami. Nous avons bien l'intention de les affronter et "
"ton village fait partie de nos plans. Tu devrais te sentir honoré."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Kromire/scenarios/1Therian_Village.cfg:243
#, fuzzy
