#, fuzzy
msgid "Reclaim your lands"
msgstr "Reprendre vos terres"

#. [message]: id=cleader
#: Kromire/scenarios/8Return.cfg:157
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Uhw... You may have broken my body, but you shall not achieve your objective."
msgstr "Argh... vous m'avez vaincu mais vous ne savourerez pas votre victoire."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Kromire/scenarios/8Return.cfg:193
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"As his strength flees his body, the wizard utters a final spell. Flames "
"spring into life throughout the castle, burning even through stone, and "
"within an hour the castle is a smoldering ruin."
msgstr ""
"Alors que ses forces le quittait, le sorcier lança un dernier sort. Des "
"flammes jaillirent dans le château de tout côté, brulant la pierre même et "
"transformant en moins d'une heure le château en ruine fumante. "

#. [message]: id=Lisaundra
#: Kromire/scenarios/8Return.cfg:198
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Anyone who would stoop to burning writings deserves to die. This abomination "
"shall not go unpunished."
msgstr ""
"Quiconque brule des écrits ne mérite que la mort. Ce crime ne restera pas "
"impuni."

#. [message]: id=cleader2
#: Kromire/scenarios/8Return.cfg:208
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Freemen of this land, do you remember the yoke your shoulders bore under the "
"reign of the vampires? If we fall to these invaders then it will once again "
"fall on you. Fight for your freedom."
msgstr ""
"Hommes libres de ce pays, souvenez-vous du joug qui pesait sur vos épaules "
"sous le règne des vampire ? SI nous tombons face à ces envahisseurs, vous "
"retomberez en esclavage. Battez-vous pour votre liberté."

#. [message]: id=Kromire
#: Kromire/scenarios/8Return.cfg:261
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Kill as few of those as is at all possible, their labor will help make us "
"strong. I will not see my lands ruined like that of Valemoi. Once the "
"celestials are defeated it will be a simple task to subject them to my will, "
"but I will need them alive."
msgstr ""
"Tuez le moins de paysans possible ! Nous avons besoin de leur travail pour "
"nous rednre fort et je ne veux pas voir mes terres ruinées comme celles de "
"Valémoï. Lorsque nous aurons vaincu les célestains, il me sera aisé de les "
"soumettre à mes volontés. Aussi me les faut-il vivants ! "

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: Kromire/scenarios/8Return.cfg:270
#, fuzzy
msgid "Kill as few peasants as possible(Bonus)"
msgstr "Tuer le moins de paysans possible (bonus)"

#. [message]: id=Kromire
#: Kromire/scenarios/8Return.cfg:286
#, fuzzy
msgid "I express my sympathies over the loss of the object of your quest."
msgstr ""
"Je vous présente toutes mes condoléances pour la perte de l'objet de votre "
"quête."

#. [message]: id=Lisaundra
#: Kromire/scenarios/8Return.cfg:290
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The scrolls the prophesies are written are not so easily destroyed. I'll "
"just have to sort through the wreckage until I find it."
msgstr ""
"La prophétie est écrite sur des parchemins qui ne se détruisent pas aussi "
"facilement. Il ne me reste qu'à fouiller dans les décombres jusqu'à ce que "
"je les trouve."

#. [message]: id=Kromire
#: Kromire/scenarios/8Return.cfg:294
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I wish you luck in your endeavor. If it is anywhere, it will be in the deep "
"catacombs near the south wall of the castle. (This is going to take her "
"forever. The catacombs, although not large, were very deep. With all the "
"supports gone, each crypt will have to be dug out separately, and she does "
"not know which is the right one)."
msgstr ""
"Je vous souhaite bonne chance dans votre entreprise. Si jamais la prophétie "
"se trouve ici, ce ne peut être que dans les profondes catacombes près du mur "
"sud du château. (Cela va l'occuper un moment. Les catacombes ne sont pas "
"étendues mais très profondes. Suite à l'effondremment de tous les plafonds, "
"les cryptes devront être déblayées une par une et elle ne sait pas quelle "
"est la bonne)."

#. [message]: id=Kromire
#: Kromire/scenarios/8Return.cfg:298
msgid ""
"(Though I would assume that nothing will stop her at this point.) Minion, "
"assemble the remaining peasants. I will reassert my power over them, as well "
"as provide fodder for the fledglings. Prepare a feast to celebrate, and "
"bring some wine for the humans, I am going to need to replenish their "
"numbers. None are to bite the humans until we are fully settled. Blood must "
"be harvested from their cattle. Leave the Windsong to their task, they are "
"not to be disturbed."
msgstr ""

